ourts from reconstruction to the new deal duke university press books  and coeditor of phantom risk scientific inference and the law mit  he is a former chairperson of the association of american law schools evidence section professor bernstein teaches products liability evidence constitutional law i and ii and scientific and expert evidence professor bernstein is a contributor to the popular weblog the volokh conspiracy search events giving llm news people finder technology mason quick links academic calendar bloomberg law campus bookstore career  academic services intranet class schedules  assignments its support center law school catalog lexisnexis listservs archives masonlive email students office  email facultystaff patriot web symplicity westlawtwen faculty  scalia law school home » faculty to  faculty faculty directory faculty news faculty journals faculty working papers faculty workshops meet our faculty search events giving llm news people finder technology mason quick links academic calendar bloomberg law campus bookstore career  academic services intranet class schedules  assignments its support center law school catalog lexisnexis listservs archives masonlive email students office  email facultystaff patriot web symplicity westlawtwen faculty directory  scalia law school home » faculty to  » directory to  faculty directories complete faculty directory full time faculty emeritus faculty adjunct faculty faculty directory full time faculty aistars sandra clinical professor and senior scholar and director of copyright research and policy of cpipalvaré helen professor of lawatkins jennifer director second year legal research writing and analysis programbernstein david university professorboardman michelle associate professor of lawbuckley francis george mason university foundation professor of lawbutler henry dean and professor of lawchiang tunjen associate professor of lawchorvat terrence professor of lawclaeys eric professor of lawcohen lloyd professor of l